    {
      "instruction": "<p>After the chicken has had an initial 10 min, remove the tray from the oven and divide the <strong>grated cheese</strong> equally over the top of each chicken thigh – these are your <strong>cheesy chicken thighs</strong></p><p>Slice your <strong>brioche style bun[s]</strong> in half, then add the <strong>brioche halves </strong>to the other side of the tray and return it to the oven for 2-3 min until the cheese has melted and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
