    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>remaining ground smoked paprika</strong> to a bowl with your <strong>mayo </strong>and the juice of<strong> half</strong> your <strong>lime[s] </strong>– this is your <strong>paprika mayo</strong></p>",
