    {
      "instruction": "<p>Spread a dollop of <strong>paprika</strong> <strong>mayo</strong> over the <strong>brioche</strong> <strong>base</strong>, then top with the <strong>cheesy chicken thighs</strong>, <strong>fajita</strong> <strong>spiced onion & pepper</strong> and the <strong>brioche lid </strong>– this is your <strong>cheesy chicken thigh fajita burger</strong></p><p>Serve the<strong> fries </strong>and <strong>remaining paprika mayo </strong>to the side and garnish with the <strong>lime wedges</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
